    <h1>Invisalign North Potomac – Clear Aligner Treatment by Experts</h1>
    <p><small>Published: June 25, 2025 | By <strong>Dr. Richard Cantwell, DDS</strong></small></p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <p>Want to straighten your teeth without the hassle of metal braces? <strong>Invisalign</strong> offers a clear, removable, and nearly invisible solution—perfect for both teens and adults. At <strong>Potomac Crown Dentistry</strong> in <strong>North Potomac, MD</strong>, Dr. Richard Cantwell provides expert Invisalign treatment tailored to your smile goals.</p>

    <h2>Why Choose Invisalign?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Virtually invisible aligners</li>
      <li>Removable for meals, brushing, and flossing</li>
      <li>Fewer visits than traditional braces</li>
      <li>Comfortable, no metal brackets or wires</li>
      <li>Customized with 3D scanning technology</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Top 1% Diamond Invisalign Provider</h2>
    <p><a href="https://potomaccrowndentistry.com/services/invisalign/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Potomac Crown Dentistry</a> is proud to be a Top 1% Diamond Invisalign Provider in North America. With years of experience and advanced iTero® digital scans, Dr. Cantwell crafts personalized treatment plans that deliver results efficiently and comfortably.</p>

    <h2>How Invisalign Works</h2>
    <p>Your journey begins with a consultation and a 3D digital scan. You’ll receive a series of clear aligners that gradually shift your teeth into position. Each aligner is worn for 1–2 weeks before switching to the next in the series.</p>

    <h2>Cost & Insurance</h2>
    <p>The cost of Invisalign at our North Potomac office ranges from $3,500 to $6,500, depending on case complexity. Many insurance plans cover a portion of Invisalign. We also offer flexible financing to make treatment accessible for every smile.</p>

    <h2>Book Your Consultation</h2>
    <p>Ready to love your smile again? <a href="https://potomaccrowndentistry.com/services/invisalign/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Schedule your Invisalign consultation</a> today with Dr. Richard Cantwell at Potomac Crown Dentistry and take the first step toward a straighter, healthier smile.</p>
